{"tid":758640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國羽球隊來台比賽　女隊員爆遭同隊國手世界冠軍性侵","createTime":"2018-07-28T01:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T03:33:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca5ee4f45f7480827b1eef8840ff88d80f999bd","tid":758640,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T01:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180727/640_b3287f6d451db5e62852c15e07b46702.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180727%2F640_b3287f6d451db5e62852c15e07b46702.jpg&h=e08c6ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">一名現居寧波的高二少女指控中國羽球世界冠軍劉堅軍、前羽球國手張偉多次利用帶隊來台灣比賽期間，涉嫌對她性騷擾、性侵。翻攝微博</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國「#MeToo」運動持續發酵，知名慈善公益人雷闖、《新周刊》創辦人孫冕、作家張弛、師範大學法學院院長趙秉志、中央電視台主持人朱軍等重量級人物接二連三被踢爆涉嫌性侵、性騷擾後，近日又有一名17歲少女在《微博》爆料，2年多前她隨中國前羽球國手、寧波市羽毛球隊教練張偉來台灣比賽時也險遭性侵，事後張偉還對外宣稱是她主動色誘，害她兩年多來鬱鬱寡歡，直到最近看見許多受害者都鼓起勇氣站了出來，她才決定公開此事，「我希望有越來越多受到侵犯的女孩子不要忍氣吞聲......。」<br />\n<br />\n從藝文界、公益界、媒體圈、學術界開始，中國「#MeToo」之火一路延燒至體育界，一名現居寧波的高二少女指控中國羽球世界冠軍劉堅軍、前羽球國手張偉多次利用帶隊來台灣比賽期間，涉嫌對她性騷擾、性侵， 「以上兩次我一直埋藏在心中，不敢公開，使我這幾年來內心壓抑，抑鬱。在親人朋友的關心與鼓勵下，我鼓起勇氣將此事公開......。」呼籲女性同胞遭遇性侵不要自責，網友看完她的自白後也紛紛留言表達聲援，「從以前的馬家軍到現在，體育圈真的太髒了！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180727/1399825/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180727%2F1399825%2F&d=6BTf8xs85qiJDV7eXNNnQ8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=006971a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180727%2F1399825%2F&h=6d99187d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180727/1399825/</a>"},{"pid":"528186a882081a2cf7547588afd3ab733ad56fc5","tid":758640,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:02:37.000Z","msg":"諗起吳帥當年點用運動員身份食ck就知見到運動員要調頭走"},{"pid":"3429b4895b5bad71b177c050e49cb46dc73f15cd","tid":758640,"uid":59699,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:04:32.000Z","msg":"笑左，中國有邊個未姦過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c326cf0915730e3e8091dfb2262052c6fe0dcce","tid":758640,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"528186a882081a2cf7547588afd3ab733ad56fc5","tid":758640,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:02:37.000Z","msg":"諗起吳帥當年點用運動員身份食ck就知見到運動員要調頭走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"你情我願都有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cca3340662ab96e31f207b641baae51d274ee38","tid":758640,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c326cf0915730e3e8091dfb2262052c6fe0dcce","tid":758640,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"528186a882081a2cf7547588afd3ab733ad56fc5","tid":758640,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:02:37.000Z","msg":"諗起吳帥當年點用運動員身份食ck就知見到運動員要調頭走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"你情我願都有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:22:33.000Z","msg":"不平等條約係唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78a98ddd0e8c23839c60f242f89eadc1e1e67cc","tid":758640,"uid":35648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3429b4895b5bad71b177c050e49cb46dc73f15cd","tid":758640,"uid":59699,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:04:32.000Z","msg":"笑左，中國有邊個未姦過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"全國鳩頭 犯有雞姦死罪"}]}